# Pull requests — pre-push checks

Before **`git push`** or **`gh pr create`**:

1. **`npm run lint`** — required; CI **`next build`** fails on ESLint errors.
2. **`npm run test:unit`** — when TypeScript/application logic changed.
3. **`npm run test`** or **`npm run test:functional`** — when APIs, Prisma, or integrations changed.

Do not open or update a PR until **`npm run lint`** exits 0.
